<div class="title">
<h1 class="title__header">Common FOI Requests</h1>
</div><!-- title -->

<div class="container">
	<div class="main">
		<div class="content">
		<p class="lead">We a duty to specify what information we publish, how it is available and whether it is free or if there is a charge. Here we have compiled the most common requests for information we recieve.</p>
		<p>If you would like any of this information translated into a difference language, Braille or audio – or if you are unable to find the information you require on this page or the rest of the site – you can send a request to the FOI team.</p>
		<p>We also recommend using our search function as well if the information can't be found here.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="complementary">
		<h4><a href="making-an-foi-request.html">Making an FOI request</a></h4>
		<p class="secondary">If you can't find the information you need here you can make an FOI request.</p>
	</div>
</div>

