			<p>It is Trust policy not to give out staff details except those in senior or public facing roles including staff names, personal email addresses or contact details. This policy helps protect Trust staff from unsolicited emails, calls or correspondence not directly related to their role and the work they are doing.  You can of course call the main Trust switchboard on 020 3299 9000.</p>
