		<div class="content">
		<h5 class="separator"><a class="headeranchor" id="About_this_information_0" href="#About_this_information_0"></a> About this information </h5>
		<p>The information is current and/or for the periods stated; We&#8217;ll publish updated information periodically. Accordingly, where we receive requests for more up to date information, We&#8217;ll apply an FOI Act Section 22 exemption (information intended for future publication) to any such FoI request received.</p>
		<p>All documents are the current versions, unless otherwise stated. If a published policy's review date is due shortly, or the review is in progress, We&#8217;ll publish the updated policy when it becomes available. Accordingly, where we receive requests for more up to date policy, We&#8217;ll apply an FOI Act Section 22 exemption (information intended for future publication) to any such FoI request received</p>
